## Composition Patterns

### Double-Border Prevention

When two Frames are adjacent, omit the shared border on one side. Example: NavLink icon Frame has all 4 borders, text Frame omits `left` so they share a single border line.

### Interactive Signalling

Accent bar next to a Frame = "you can interact with this". Place both inside a Button wrapper. The Button sets CSS custom properties on hover that both Frame and Accent respond to.

### Layering on Cube Faces

FaceGrid uses `position: relative` with `overflow: hidden`. Stack content by using multiple `absolute inset-0` children. Use `mix-blend-mode` and `opacity` for visual effects. Later layers sit on top of earlier ones.

